{"tid":794013,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南泡支那偷鞋單嘢，有冇方法攪大佢？","createTime":"2018-08-25T22:27:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-16T09:40:05.000Z","uid":143499,"like":242,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"90ec53b4c5f2614c4c7a2773e5e7b1fec9879fe9","tid":794013,"uid":143499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T22:27:11.000Z","msg":"香港人平日畀支那恰到上心口，我哋還唔到擊因為，佢哋擁有國家機器我哋只可以盡力而為除非革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係今次呢單嘢喺國際賽事發生， 應該可以寫信去主辦單位投訴，而且南韓有明顯動機去損害香港參賽者嘅利益，如果我哋咁多位巴打絲打就手旁觀當食花生咁睇戲， 咁我祝我哋一世俾支那統治<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好冷嘲熱諷怕炒車或者將個責任推翻去自己友， 因為南泡選手早已經承認佢教練攞咗香港選手對釘鞋，呢啲行為分分鐘嚴重過食禁藥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果泡菜支那為咗出線，而無所不其極， 咁我哋一定要用盡方法討回公道奶返佢落嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1ed467127beaaf678af215e351b54dc73fcdae","tid":794013,"uid":53466,"like":9,"dislike":339,"score":-330,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T22:35:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b99322c530c4cedef7a1c8eeb6f7b4d215965e0e","tid":794013,"uid":39547,"like":94,"dislike":2,"score":92,"quote":{"pid":"4c1ed467127beaaf678af215e351b54dc73fcdae","tid":794013,"uid":53466,"like":9,"dislike":339,"score":-330,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T22:35:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T22:38:08.000Z","msg":"咁就唔可以投訴？"},{"pid":"0a44556be62c5d00fa1f254a7cd1c44e72995574","tid":794013,"uid":143499,"like":73,"dislike":1,"score":72,"quote":{"pid":"4c1ed467127beaaf678af215e351b54dc73fcdae","tid":794013,"uid":53466,"like":9,"dislike":339,"score":-330,"citedBy":10,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T22:35:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T22:44:19.000Z","msg":"如果畫畫比賽對方一個唔小心成杯咖啡咗落嚟幅畫度咁又點計？"},{"pid":"1991d75fd2f7941882445eb1cb66b4b36f4ec419","tid":794013,"uid":53466,"like":2,"dislike":83,"score":-81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-08-25T22:44: